data.description: Welcome to 4333 Norfolk Ave, a charming end-of-unit townhome offering two fantastic units that combine modern living with convenience. Each unit features two bedrooms and one bathroom, making it perfect for comfortable living or a savvy investment opportunity. The open kitchens in both units are a chef's dream, complete with stainless steel appliances and ample cabinet space. Enjoy the ease of in-unit laundry facilities in both units. The spacious living and dining areas in each unit provide plenty of room for relaxation and entertainment. This property boasts a shared outdoor space for gatherings and summer parties. Located in a prime area with easy access to dining and transportation, 4333 Norfolk Ave is an ideal choice for those seeking a versatile property that offers both functionality and convenience. Don't miss the opportunity to make this rare gem your new home or investment property. Both units are currently rented with Unit 1 being a long standing tenant paying $900/month and Unit 2 paying $1,100/month. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and discover the charm and potential this property has to offer.
